<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
  <title>Reset your password</title>
  <style>
    body{margin:0;padding:0;background:#06080d;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;color:#e2e8f0}
    .wrap{max-width:540px;margin:40px auto;background:#111827;border:1px solid #1e293b;border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden}
    .header{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#111827,#162032);padding:28px 32px;border-bottom:1px solid #1e293b;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
    .logo{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#f59e0b}
    .body{padding:36px}
    h2{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 12px}
    p{color:#94a3b8;font-size:14px;line-height:1.65;margin:0 0 14px}
    .warning{background:rgba(245,158,11,0.08);border:1px solid rgba(245,158,11,0.25);border-radius:8px;padding:14px;margin:20px 0;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8}
    .cta{display:block;background:#f59e0b;color:#000;text-align:center;padding:14px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;text-decoration:none;margin:20px 0}
    .link-box{background:#162032;border:1px solid #253044;border-radius:8px;padding:12px;word-break:break-all;font-size:12px;color:#94a3b8;margin-top:12px}
    .footer{padding:18px 32px;border-top:1px solid #1e293b;text-align:center;font-size:12px;color:#475569}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="header">
      <span style="font-size:26px">☀️</span>
      <div class="logo">Solar Maket</div>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <h2>🔒 Reset Your Password</h2>
      <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>We received a request to reset the password for your Solar Maket account. Click the button below to set a new password:</p>
      <a href="{{resetUrl}}" class="cta">Reset My Password</a>
      <div class="warning">
        ⏰ <strong>This link expires in 1 hour.</strong> If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email — your account remains secure.
      </div>
      <p>If the button doesn't work, copy and paste this link into your browser:</p>
      <div class="link-box">{{resetUrl}}</div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">© {{year}} Solar Maket Nigeria Ltd. All rights reserved.</div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
